{"tid":2017527,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"藍奕邦爆粗鬧阿倫廢老","createTime":"2020-05-15T06:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T07:15:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"87e8ed0144083a004a8abac66eddd28d6822df87","tid":2017527,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T06:53:56.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200515/VVMLVHIBGRYM4OVD2GW6CGKEBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200515%2FVVMLVHIBGRYM4OVD2GW6CGKEBE%2F&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRQi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=9fea1683\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200515%2FVVMLVHIBGRYM4OVD2GW6CGKEBE%2F&h=7571512a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200515/VVMLVHIBGRYM4OVD2GW6CGKEBE/</a><br />\n<br />\n藍奕邦爆粗鬧阿倫廢老<br />\n<br />\n藍奕邦早前在社交平台宣佈跟環球唱片結束六年賓主關係後，向來敢言的他，去年一直留意香港的逆權運動，對於日前譚詠麟（阿倫）和鍾鎮濤回應為撐警令歌迷反感遭割席一事，阿倫說：「其實我們立場只有一個，只不過是有些人不尊重我們。」藍奕邦前晚在Ig限時動態爆粗指摘曾是同屬環球的阿倫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200515/large/1589461174_f4a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200515%2Flarge%2F1589461174_f4a8.jpg&h=0435e43d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍奕邦（圖）前晚在Ig限時動態中爆粗指摘阿倫。<br />\n<br />\n於藍奕邦的Ig限時動態中，他引述報道狂鬧：「收X啦死廢老，見你前面憎你後面，死奶。。。。。。。？你有尊重過香港人咩？你幫一班。。。。。。。啲去死啦。」跟着還標籤：「。。。。。。。。。。」《蘋果》昨日聯絡藍奕邦，他回覆：「冇特別回應了。多謝。祝你身體健康！」<br />\n採訪：皓騫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200515/large/1589461173_090d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200515%2Flarge%2F1589461173_090d.jpg&h=7b13cd0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚詠麟。資料圖片"},{"pid":"d96f820f9e1dfb8a0161f9faebabd7af09cbadb8","tid":2017527,"uid":235531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}